Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.73,0:00:03.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wealth, fame, power...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.76,0:00:05.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gold Roger,\Nthe King of the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.66,0:00:07.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,attained everything\Nthis world has to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.97,0:00:11.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The words he uttered just before\Nhis death drove people to the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.84,0:00:15.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My treasure?\NIf you want it, you can have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.67,0:00:19.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find it! I left everything\Nthis world has to offer there!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.85,0:00:26.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so men head for the\NGrand Line in pursuit of their dreams!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.59,0:00:30.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world has truly\Nentered a Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.49,0:00:35.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to gather up\Nall our dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.86,0:00:41.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and set out in search\Nof something to find
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.77,0:00:43.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ONE PIECE!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.97,0:00:53.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Compasses only cause delays
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.61,0:00:59.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Delirious with fever,\NI take the helm
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.35,0:01:11.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the dusty treasure map has\Nbeen verified, it's not a legend!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.46,0:01:17.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When it comes to personal storms,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.17,0:01:22.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,simply ride aboard\Nsomeone else's biorhythm
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.47,0:01:26.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and pretend it isn't there!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.14,0:01:31.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to gather up\Nall our dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.65,0:01:37.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and set out in search\Nof something to find
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.36,0:01:43.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A coin in my pocket,\Nand do you wanna be my friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.60,0:01:48.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are, We are on the cruise!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.97,0:01:50.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.04,0:01:57.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These are just in the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.28,0:02:03.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--There it is...\N-- "Cat Burglar"...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.18,0:02:07.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not that great at the\NOne-Sword Style, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.42,0:02:09.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Butchie!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.89,0:02:12.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Let's do it, Siam!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.60,0:02:20.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! If I just had another sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.47,0:02:24.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I can just get Zoro his swords...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.67,0:02:31.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you need swords for?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.25,0:02:41.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Luffy, Back in Action!\NMiss Kaya's Desperate Resistance"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.96,0:03:25.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To think that these brats\Nhave held you back...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.43,0:03:29.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How the Black Cat Pirates have fallen...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.17,0:03:35.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right... Jango?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.24,0:03:48.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-B-But... you said letting that kid\Ngo wouldn't cause any problems!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.96,0:03:54.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I did say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.29,0:04:01.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But so what? We knew he was\Ngoing to try to stand up to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.57,0:04:04.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The only thing I didn't count on...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.24,0:04:07.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...was you guys' feebleness!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.51,0:04:10.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,U-Us, feeble?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.14,0:04:12.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who're you calling feeble?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.14,0:04:15.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch what you say, Captain Kuro!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.95,0:04:19.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you were strong before!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.65,0:04:21.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that was three years ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.82,0:04:27.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like we partied while you\Nlived the easy life in this village!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.09,0:04:33.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,'As right! We've attacked lotsa\Ntowns and sunk lotsa pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.67,0:04:37.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your point being...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.40,0:04:40.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've done nothing for three years!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.44,0:04:44.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way you can beat\Nthe Meowban Brothers of today!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.08,0:04:50.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Stop! Butchie! Siam!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.89,0:04:59.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not our captain anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.62,0:05:02.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but we're gonna kill ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.25,0:05:27.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-When did he get behind them?!\NAnd those weapons...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.75,0:05:32.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.52,0:05:35.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you going to kill?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.99,0:05:38.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--He snuck...\N--...behind us!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.13,0:05:44.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Eh?!\N--He's gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.14,0:05:53.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There it is! The Pussy Foot Maneuver...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.65,0:05:55.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pussy Foot Maneuver?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.75,0:06:04.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.69,0:06:13.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I do feel a bit of sluggishness.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.97,0:06:15.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's handling them like kids,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.27,0:06:19.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,after they had the upper hand\Nagainst Zoro and his one sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.21,0:06:25.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That man's "Pussy Foot Maneuver"\Nis a silent movement technique.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.28,0:06:31.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even a group of 50 assassins would\Nbe killed before sensing him!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.42,0:06:36.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way we can escape his plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.19,0:06:42.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I got chills after seeing that\Nhabit of his again three years after!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.76,0:06:46.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His odd way of lifting his glasses\Nto avoid cutting his own face
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.20,0:06:48.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,with those Cat Claws...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.67,0:06:51.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Clear proof that he hasn't\Nforgotten how to fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.72,0:07:15.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems I've grown\Na bit good-natured myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.16,0:07:20.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,during my last three years on dry land...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.63,0:07:23.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give you five minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.90,0:07:29.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you can't take care of\Nthings here in five minutes...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.64,0:07:33.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...then I'll kill every last one of you...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.78,0:07:39.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...with my own two hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.53,0:07:50.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Five minutes...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.09,0:07:52.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Five minutes should be enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.60,0:07:59.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Him! If we just beat him,\Nwe can get past this hill!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.58,0:08:09.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We had the upper hand\Nagainst him just now!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.95,0:08:12.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll cut him up in five minutes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.52,0:08:16.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're counting on you,\NMeowban Brothers!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.39,0:08:20.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.56,0:08:27.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What?!\N--H-Hey, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.10,0:08:30.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now you're kicking my swords, too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.50,0:08:32.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's my "thanks"?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.94,0:08:35.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.47,0:08:37.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.74,0:08:42.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use!\NThree swords won't help any!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.41,0:08:44.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your skill's still the same!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.25,0:08:47.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tiger...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.52,0:08:53.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't get it, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.32,0:08:54.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Trap!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.43,0:09:02.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Four minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.10,0:09:08.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just having three swords is different
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.87,0:09:11.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,from knowing the Three-Sword Style!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.72,0:09:22.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's strong...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.39,0:09:28.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One hit...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.17,0:09:41.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-He beat the Meowban\NBrothers in one hit!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.82,0:09:54.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.42,0:10:01.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll crush every last one of you\Nbefore your five minutes are up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.67,0:10:15.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Three minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.81,0:10:25.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'll... slaughter him...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.65,0:10:30.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C-Captain...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.72,0:10:34.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hypnotize me...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.86,0:10:38.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,P-Please, Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.96,0:10:42.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's alive. You do sloppy work.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.00,0:10:49.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His tough fat saved him, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.53,0:11:11.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get 'im, Butchie!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.97,0:11:19.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More hypnosis?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.11,0:11:27.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This guy means trouble! He could\Nalready crack the ground apart!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.45,0:11:32.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happens when he's powered up?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.09,0:11:43.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is my chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.76,0:11:47.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I gotta wake him up while I still can!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.10,0:11:52.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that crafty girl up to now?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.01,0:12:02.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's seriously hurt,\Nand he's just sleeping!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.52,0:12:07.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.23,0:12:16.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.86,0:12:18.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami! Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.37,0:12:28.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Two minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.39,0:12:46.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.12,0:12:48.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami! Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.10,0:12:53.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Split in two!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.10,0:12:56.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dodge it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.54,0:13:00.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What the...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.24,0:13:05.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A chakram! It wasn't\Njust a hypnosis tool?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.28,0:13:10.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami! How dare you stomp on my face?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.62,0:13:22.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-He's alive?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.46,0:13:27.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't tell if he has bad or good timing...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.44,0:13:38.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L-Luffy...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.21,0:13:44.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.88,0:13:46.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oww...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.85,0:13:50.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.76,0:13:53.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-He's alive again!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.12,0:13:58.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--This is bad!\N--Five minutes is impossible now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.56,0:14:01.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami! That hurts, you jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.63,0:14:03.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-That wasn't me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.87,0:14:06.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't me--
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.91,0:14:12.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-Nami! Did you hurt your shoulder?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.58,0:14:15.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's nothing. I'm fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.71,0:14:22.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've done everything I can for now,\Nso I leave the rest to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.42,0:14:28.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We absolutely can't\Nafford to lose this fight...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.33,0:14:29.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.56,0:14:31.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For the treasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.37,0:14:37.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll all work out in the end!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.64,0:14:41.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Try hard! For my treasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.11,0:14:44.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! That sounds like you, alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.51,0:14:48.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.28,0:14:52.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't be serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.15,0:14:54.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not even Captain Jango\Nand Butchie-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.79,0:14:58.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...can finish them in one minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.40,0:15:17.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Butchie! There's no time to think!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.07,0:15:19.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kill that haramaki bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.28,0:15:23.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'll handle that weird kid...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.09,0:15:32.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll kill Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.90,0:15:41.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's about time for everyone to die now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.81,0:15:58.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? That bad butler is here too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.95,0:16:00.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't he...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.72,0:16:05.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't he fall off that cliff and die?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.02,0:16:07.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.74,0:16:20.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't approach me...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.81,0:16:25.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...from behind!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.94,0:16:28.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaya!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.16,0:16:47.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,U-Usopp-san! Are you okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.77,0:16:51.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,K-Kaya... What are you doing here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.34,0:16:53.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so sorry, Usopp-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.57,0:16:56.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know you may not accept my apology,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.37,0:16:59.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I just couldn't believe it...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.01,0:17:01.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,K-Klahadore, a pirate...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.55,0:17:05.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-Never mind that!\NWhy are you here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.28,0:17:07.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I told you to run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.22,0:17:09.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your life is in danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.59,0:17:13.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you're fighting!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.89,0:17:18.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even after I treated you so horribly\Nand you've been hurt so much,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.60,0:17:22.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you're still fighting for me! So I...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.50,0:17:25.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Kaya...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.37,0:17:28.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.27,0:17:33.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Stop this...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.28,0:17:39.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop this, Klahadore!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.09,0:17:49.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Merry told me everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.53,0:17:57.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that the girl from the mansion?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.30,0:18:00.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meaning she's the plan's final target?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.24,0:18:02.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then there's no need to\Ngo to the village now?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.97,0:18:05.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We just need to kill her, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.31,0:18:12.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Klahadore, please! If you want\Nmy fortune, you can have it all!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.75,0:18:17.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just please leave\Nthis village! Right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.05,0:18:21.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will gladly accept it... but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.66,0:18:26.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...there's one other\Nthing I want, you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.40,0:18:32.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What I want...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.27,0:18:35.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...is peace of mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.14,0:18:37.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Peace?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.74,0:18:42.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I want simple peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.61,0:18:46.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I find the villagers' trust that I've\Nfostered these past three years
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.62,0:18:52.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to be nice and comfortable now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.12,0:18:58.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I want to have that\Npeace of mind forever...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.67,0:19:07.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.87,0:19:14.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I will have that peace!\NAnd your fortune...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.31,0:19:17.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In short, pirates will\Ncome to the village!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.78,0:19:21.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.25,0:19:24.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...you will leave your will and die!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.79,0:19:28.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These two things are absolute.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.83,0:19:31.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.83,0:19:34.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You're not...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.80,0:19:36.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run! Run away, Kaya!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.73,0:19:40.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no use talking to him! Run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.07,0:19:46.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You're not Klahadore.\NYou're not Klahadore...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.31,0:19:48.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaya...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.22,0:19:54.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave this village!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.15,0:19:58.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... You'd point a gun at me...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.32,0:20:01.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave this minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.29,0:20:07.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. You've certainly grown\Na lot these past three years...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.80,0:20:10.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Miss Kaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.87,0:20:17.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you remember? So much\Nhas happened in three years...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.31,0:20:21.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We spent so much time together,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.71,0:20:26.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,even before your parents passed\Naway and you became bedridden...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.42,0:20:28.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So much time...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.62,0:20:34.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So many memories...\NTogether we suffered...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.39,0:20:38.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Together we rejoiced...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.13,0:20:41.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,K-Klahadore...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.63,0:20:44.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I would visit the city with you,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.44,0:20:48.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and whenever you had a fever,\NI constantly looked after you...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.21,0:20:54.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You listened to my stories so happily...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.38,0:20:58.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I devoted myself to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.58,0:21:00.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For so long...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.32,0:21:05.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, for so long, I endured it...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.92,0:21:14.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it was all so that\NI could kill you today...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.64,0:21:24.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I, a man once known as Captain Kuro,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.94,0:21:30.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,had to smile humbly\Nfor some snot-nosed girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.05,0:21:34.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I went against my nature\Nand sucked up to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.89,0:21:41.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.02,0:21:45.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you understand these daily insults?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.33,0:21:50.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you understand this man\Nonce known as Captain Kuro?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.14,0:22:00.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kuro!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.05,0:22:09.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.59,0:22:15.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I still owe you for hitting me...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.53,0:22:17.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.39,0:22:22.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You hit me with all\Nyour might, as I recall...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.22,0:22:52.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you hate getting hit that much,\NI got a hundred more punches for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.03,0:23:09.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I was little, I had\Na vision of a treasure map
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.28,0:23:16.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I always searched\Nfor that miraculous place
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.22,0:23:23.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,before someone else could\Nbeat me to it
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.06,0:23:37.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the world is going to change
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.54,0:23:44.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,before I can even attain my dream
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.55,0:23:51.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then take me to the time\Nwhen I knew nothing
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.62,0:24:05.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so that my memories won't fade
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.37,0:24:14.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp! You go save Miss Kaya!\NLeave the bad butler to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.58,0:24:17.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What a helplessly evil guy!\N--I don't plan to help him, though!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.68,0:24:19.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm goin' after that hypno-freak!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.38,0:24:22.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kuro! You're not cut out to be a pirate!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.29,0:24:25.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My ambition is much greater than yours!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.29,0:24:26.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.76,0:24:30.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Beat Kuro! Usopp the Man's\NTearful Resolve!"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.39,0:24:33.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
